{"word":"G2013 - ἐπιτυγχάνω - epitynchánō - ep-ee-toong-khan'-o - Obtain","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιτυγχάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epitynchánō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-toong-khan'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Obtain</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அடைந்திரு, பெறு"},{"paragraph":"1. to light or hit upon any person or thing"},{"paragraph":"2. to attain to, obtain"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G5177 - τυγχάνω - tynchánō - toong-khan'-o/5177\">G5177</a>; to <i>chance upon</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>attain:</i> - obtain.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}